00:06:31.391 --> 00:06:33.555 line:85% position:50% size:80%
W ODDALI ŚWIST WIATRU

00:06:33.675 --> 00:06:35.678 line:85% position:50% size:80%
Paskudny wiatr.

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:39.485 align:middle line:79% position:50% size:80%
